                    <span>This terrific book explains how to plan and execute a product platform which leads to a series of continuously improved products. We have used the system at our company to plan and evolve both software products and services. We have been able to spin out many different services that seem very different, but were really variations on the basic platform we had previously built. We can provide tailored solutions for clients with less than 10% of the effort that went into the initial platform development.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A new follow up to the Power of Product Platforms coming....</div>
